<item>
            <title>[SOLR-11715] Spatial Search ref-guide fixes</title>
                <link>https://issues.apache.org/jira/browse/SOLR-11715</link>
                <project id="12310230" key="SOLR">Solr</project>
                    <description>&lt;p&gt;Was doing a demo of spatial search and ran into the following problems:&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;ol&gt;
	&lt;li&gt;Some blocks of code were not formatted properly, hence losing the &lt;tt&gt;&lt;b&gt;:&lt;/b&gt;&lt;/tt&gt; parameters. Example: &lt;a href=&quot;https://lucene.apache.org/solr/guide/6_6/spatial-search.html#SpatialSearch-bbox&quot; class=&quot;external-link&quot; target=&quot;_blank&quot; rel=&quot;nofollow noopener&quot;&gt;https://lucene.apache.org/solr/guide/6_6/spatial-search.html#SpatialSearch-bbox&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
	&lt;li&gt;The query mentioned for geodist section didn&apos;t actually return the scores. Need to add an fl parameter there. &lt;a href=&quot;https://lucene.apache.org/solr/guide/6_6/spatial-search.html#SpatialSearch-geodist&quot; class=&quot;external-link&quot; target=&quot;_blank&quot; rel=&quot;nofollow noopener&quot;&gt;https://lucene.apache.org/solr/guide/6_6/spatial-search.html#SpatialSearch-geodist&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ol&gt;
</description>
