                            <comment id="16348817" author="ctargett" created="Thu, 1 Feb 2018 16:05:52 +0000"  >&lt;p&gt;I fixed the examples similar to how I described in my earlier comment so they now appear correctly throughout the doc (I checked all of them to be sure). I also added the fl param to the geodist query as in Ishan&apos;s patch. So while I didn&apos;t use his patch, I incorporated some of its changes in my commits.&lt;/p&gt;</comment>
